
 - more help
 - full path of the executable: see smaps, most likely the first entry.
   Match with the name from stat, which is max. 15 characters long.
 - automatically refresh.
 - tree refresh: try not to disturb the existing tree, i.e. add and remove
   new/vanished entries, but otherwise don't change.  Note that processes
   might reparent; in this case, move to the new position.
